      <h1 class='title'>Highways Agency</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 30 March 2004 vol 419 cc86-7WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_86ws' title='Col. 86WS &mdash; HC Deb 30 March 2004 vol 419 c86WS' name='column_86ws' href='#column_86ws' rel='bookmark'>86WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0419P2-00720'>
        <a name='S6CV0419P2_20040330_CWS_4'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-jamieson' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0419P2_20040330_CWS_4' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Jamieson' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-jamieson" title="Mr David Jamieson">The Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State for Transport (Mr. David Jamieson)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0419P2-00720">The Highways Agency's 2004&#x2013;05 business plan is published today and contains seven key targets for the Agency to deliver by 31 March 2005. These are:</p><p id="S6CV0419P2-00721">
          <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_87ws' title='Col. 87WS &mdash; HC Deb 30 March 2004 vol 419 c87WS' name='column_87ws' href='#column_87ws' rel='bookmark'>87WS</a>
          Explanatory notes against each of these indicators are provided in the business plan, copies of which have been placed in the Libraries of both Houses.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
